		      	<h6>Buying FlipCoins with Ether</h6>
			      <p class="paragraph center lg" style="text-align:left!important;">
			      	If you already have a wallet, skip to Step 3.<br><br>
			      	1. Go to <a href="https://www.myetherwallet.com">MyEtherWallet</a> and follow the instructions in "Create New Wallet" (be sure to read carefully).<br><br>
					 		2. Next, add funds to your wallet (there are many alternatives for doing so, e.g. Gemini or Coinbase).<br><br>
					 		3. Click on the "Send Ether & Tokens" tab and enter your Private Key (it's a long string of characters & numbers - you should have saved this).<br><br>
					 		4. Enter the contract address (see above) in the "To Address" field (this is the address of the FlipCoin crowdsale on the Ethereum Network!)<br><br>
					 		5. Enter the amount of ETH you'd like to exchange for FlipCoins.<br><br>
					 		6. Set your gas limit to 200,000 (just to be safe).<br><br>
					 		7. Click "Generate Transaction".<br><br>
					 		8. Finally, click "Send Transaction" and confirm!
					 	</p>
